name: Jason Wong
tagline: Modestly More Than Meets the Eye
body:
### What's this?

This is a quick first stab at my personal GitHub page.  If you'd like to know me better, http://www.jasonwong.org

I'm the founder of [i5labs](http://www.i5labs.com), one of the first Rails consultancies.  We've developed applications for Global 2000 companies, gaming companies, and government. My experience creates a solution that works for you.

### Languages & Frameworks
Ruby, Rails, JavaScript, Jquery, RSpec, HTML, (S)CSS
